text.section:
Morgan State University:
Has the responsibility, with other educational institutions, for providing higher education research and graduate study in the Baltimore area;
Is the State's public urban university with a mission of instruction, research, and service;
Offers baccalaureate and graduate degrees in the arts and sciences;
Emphasizes an education addressing urban concerns; and
Offers the professional and graduate programs approved by its Board of Regents and the Maryland Higher Education Commission.
